{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<xsl:key>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/key","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>&lt;xsl:key&gt;</code>要素は、<code>key( )</code>関数を使用してスタイルシートの他の場所で使用できる名前付きキーを宣言します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;xsl:key name=NAME match=EXPRESSION\n\tuse=EXPRESSION /&gt; </pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"required_attributes","title":"必須属性","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n <dd>このキーの名前を指定します。QName でなければなりません。</dd>\n <dt id=\"match\"><code>match</code></dt>\n <dd>このキーが適用可能なノードを定義します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"use\"><code>use</code></dt>\n <dd>適用可能な各ノードのキーの値を決定するために使用される XPath 式を指定します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"optional_attributes","title":"任意属性","isH3":true,"content":"<p>なし</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"type","title":"タイプ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>最上位は <code>&lt;xsl:stylesheet&gt;</code> または <code>&lt;xsl:transform&gt;</code> の子である必要があります。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p>XSLT, section 12.2.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko のサポート","isH3":true,"content":"<p>サポート済み</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"<xsl:key>要素は、key( )関数を使用してスタイルシートの他の場所で使用できる名前付きキーを宣言します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<xsl:key>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"key","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"key","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"key","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"key","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xslt/element/key","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xslt/element/key/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT","title":"XSLT: 拡張可能なスタイルシートの言語変換"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element","title":"XSLT 要素リファレンス"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/key","title":"<xsl:key>"}],"pageTitle":"<xsl:key> - XSLT: 拡張可能なスタイルシートの言語変換 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}